  "description": "Notifications engine observability. Covers the unread backlog (notifications_active_unread_gauge), the new-episode detector (run outcomes, scan breadth via notifications_detector_combos_scanned, run duration histogram), the hourly stale-relevance invalidation job (notifications_stale_invalidated_total), and the service DB pool. All metrics emitted by services/notifications. The notifications job is scraped via docker/prometheus/prometheus.yml.",
